// Man page for ports
manPorts="PORTS(1)                         X Shell Manual                         PORTS(1)

<b>NAME</b>
    ports - List open ports on system
<b>SYNOPSIS</b>
    <b>ports</b>
<b>DESCRIPTION</b>
    Display all open network ports on the current system.
    Shows port numbers and associated services.
<b>EXAMPLE:</b>
    <color=#e4ff34># View Open Ports</color>
    <b>ports</b>
    List all open ports
<b>SEE ALSO</b>
    <b>scan</b>, <b>nmap</b>, <b>pp</b>"